Cationic sigma-phenylplatinum(II) complexes with carboxylic acid functionality: pK(a) determinations and x-ray structures. The preparation and characterization of a novel series of cationic sigma-phenylplatinum(II) complexes of the type trans-[Pt(sigma-C(6)H(5))(L)(2)A]OTf (A = picolinic acid, L = PPh(3) (4) and PMePh(2) (7) A = nicotinic acid, L = PPh(3) (5) and PMePh(2) (8)